Name: Name
Description: A name for the Classification Family. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the ClassificationFamily. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the content and purpose of the ClassificationFamily. May be expressed in multiple languages and supports the use of structured content.

Name: ClassificationSeriesReference
Description: A Classification Family may refer to a number of Classification Series. TypeOfObject should be set to ClassificationSeries.
